---
layout: layouts/app.njk
title: "Welcome"
description: "Three-step guided setup — create a profile, add your first accounts, pick a starter category template. The fastest path from empty to a working budget."
permalink: /app/welcome/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---
<div class="app-page" x-data="welcomeWizard()" x-init="init()">
  <header class="app-page__header">
    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">Welcome</p>
      <h1 class="app-page__title">Three steps to a working budget</h1>
      <p class="app-page__lead">
        We'll create a profile, drop in your everyday accounts, and seed a category list you can edit later. The whole thing is local — nothing leaves your browser.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" href="/app/" data-tip="Skip the wizard and go straight to the dashboard.">Skip for now</a>
  </header>

  <ol class="welcome-steps">
    <li class="welcome-step" :class="stepClass(1)">
      <header class="welcome-step__head">
        <span class="welcome-step__num">1</span>
        <h2 class="welcome-step__title">Name your profile</h2>
        <span class="welcome-step__status" x-text="stepStatus(1)"></span>
      </header>
      <div class="welcome-step__body" x-show="step >= 1" x-cloak>
        <p>One profile per budget — most people use one for personal money and a second for a household or side business.</p>
        <form @submit.prevent="createProfile()" class="cluster" style="gap: var(--space-sm);">
          <input class="input" type="text" x-model="profileName" placeholder="Personal, Household, Side business…" required>
          <button class="btn btn--primary" type="submit" :disabled="!profileName.trim()">Create profile</button>
        </form>
        <p class="welcome-step__hint" x-show="$store.budget.profile" x-cloak>
          Active profile: <strong x-text="$store.budget.profile?.name"></strong>. Continue below.
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="welcome-step" :class="stepClass(2)">
      <header class="welcome-step__head">
        <span class="welcome-step__num">2</span>
        <h2 class="welcome-step__title">Add your everyday accounts</h2>
        <span class="welcome-step__status" x-text="stepStatus(2)"></span>
      </header>
      <div class="welcome-step__body" x-show="step >= 2" x-cloak>
        <p>Start with checking + savings + any credit cards. You can add tracking accounts (investments, loans) later.</p>
        <template x-for="(row, i) in accountDrafts" :key="i">
          <div class="cluster" style="gap: var(--space-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">
            <input class="input" type="text" x-model="row.name" placeholder="Account name (e.g. Chase Checking)" style="flex: 1;">
            <select class="select" x-model="row.type">
              <template x-for="t in $store.budget.ACCOUNT_TYPES" :key="t.value">
                <option :value="t.value" x-text="t.label"></option>
              </template>
            </select>
            <input class="input" type="text" x-model="row.balance" placeholder="0.00" inputmode="decimal" style="width: 7rem;">
            <button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" type="button" @click="removeDraft(i)" x-show="accountDrafts.length > 1">Remove</button>
          </div>
        </template>
        <div class="cluster">
          <button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" type="button" @click="addDraft()">+ Add another</button>
          <button class="btn btn--primary" type="button" @click="createAccounts()" :disabled="!hasValidDraft()">Add these accounts</button>
        </div>
        <p class="welcome-step__hint" x-show="$store.budget.profile?.accounts.length" x-cloak>
          <span x-text="$store.budget.profile?.accounts.length"></span> account<span x-text="$store.budget.profile?.accounts.length === 1 ? '' : 's'"></span> created.
        </p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="welcome-step" :class="stepClass(3)">
      <header class="welcome-step__head">
        <span class="welcome-step__num">3</span>
        <h2 class="welcome-step__title">Pick a starter category template</h2>
        <span class="welcome-step__status" x-text="stepStatus(3)"></span>
      </header>
      <div class="welcome-step__body" x-show="step >= 3" x-cloak>
        <p>Each template seeds a few groups + categories you can rename, reorder, or delete. None of these are permanent.</p>
        <div class="welcome-templates">
          <template x-for="tpl in templates" :key="tpl.id">
            <button type="button" class="welcome-template"
                    :class="selectedTemplate === tpl.id ? 'is-selected' : ''"
                    @click="selectedTemplate = tpl.id">
              <h3 x-text="tpl.label"></h3>
              <p x-text="tpl.description"></p>
              <ul>
                <template x-for="g in tpl.preview" :key="g">
                  <li x-text="g"></li>
                </template>
              </ul>
            </button>
          </template>
        </div>
        <div class="cluster" style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
          <button class="btn btn--ghost btn--sm" type="button" @click="skipTemplate()">Skip — I'll build my own</button>
          <button class="btn btn--primary" type="button" @click="applyTemplate()" :disabled="!selectedTemplate">Apply template</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>

  <section class="card" x-show="step >= 4" x-cloak style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
    <h2 class="card__title">You're set up.</h2>
    <p style="color: var(--fg-muted);">Profile, accounts, and categories are all in place. Open the dashboard to see your numbers, or jump straight to the budget to assign your first dollars.</p>
    <div class="cluster" style="margin-top: var(--space-sm);">
      <a class="btn btn--primary" href="/app/">Open dashboard</a>
      <a class="btn btn--secondary" href="/app/budget/">Open budget</a>
      <a class="btn btn--ghost" href="/app/register/">Enter your first transaction</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<script>
function welcomeWizard() {
  return {
    step: 1,
    profileName: "",
    accountDrafts: [
      { name: "", type: "checking", balance: "" },
      { name: "", type: "savings", balance: "" },
    ],
    selectedTemplate: "",
    templates: [
      {
        id: "essentials",
        label: "Essentials",
        description: "Bare-minimum 4-group set. Best when you want to add categories as you discover them.",
        preview: ["Immediate Obligations", "Quality of Life", "Just for Fun", "Savings"],
        groups: [
          { name: "Immediate Obligations", cats: ["Rent / Mortgage", "Electric", "Internet", "Groceries", "Transportation"] },
          { name: "Quality of Life",      cats: ["Insurance", "Subscriptions", "Phone", "Dining out"] },
          { name: "Just for Fun",          cats: ["Hobbies", "Entertainment", "Travel"] },
          { name: "Savings",               cats: ["Emergency fund", "Vacation", "Holidays"] },
        ],
      },
      {
        id: "household",
        label: "Household",
        description: "Family-budget shape — keeps daily, kid, and pet costs in their own buckets.",
        preview: ["Home", "Kids", "Food", "Transport", "Pets", "Savings"],
        groups: [
          { name: "Home",      cats: ["Mortgage / Rent", "Utilities", "Internet", "Home maintenance", "Property tax"] },
          { name: "Kids",      cats: ["Childcare", "Activities", "School", "Clothing"] },
          { name: "Food",      cats: ["Groceries", "Dining out", "Coffee"] },
          { name: "Transport", cats: ["Fuel", "Car insurance", "Maintenance", "Transit"] },
          { name: "Pets",      cats: ["Food", "Vet", "Grooming"] },
          { name: "Savings",   cats: ["Emergency fund", "College", "Vacation"] },
        ],
      },
      {
        id: "freelance",
        label: "Freelance / side income",
        description: "Adds tax-set-aside + business expense buckets. Pairs with a Tracking account for taxes payable.",
        preview: ["Business", "Taxes", "Personal", "Savings"],
        groups: [
          { name: "Business", cats: ["Software", "Hardware", "Subcontractors", "Marketing", "Office supplies"] },
          { name: "Taxes",    cats: ["Federal estimated", "State estimated", "Self-employment"] },
          { name: "Personal", cats: ["Rent / Mortgage", "Groceries", "Utilities", "Transport", "Dining out"] },
          { name: "Savings",  cats: ["Emergency fund", "Retirement", "Hardware fund"] },
        ],
      },
    ],

    init() {
      /* Advance to the highest already-satisfied step on revisit so a
         returning user lands on the work they still have left. */
      var s = this.$store.budget;
      if (s.profile) {
        this.step = Math.max(this.step, 2);
        if (s.profile.accounts.length) this.step = Math.max(this.step, 3);
        if (s.profile.categories.length) this.step = Math.max(this.step, 4);
      }
    },
    stepClass(n) {
      if (this.step > n) return "is-done";
      if (this.step === n) return "is-current";
      return "is-future";
    },
    stepStatus(n) {
      if (this.step > n) return "Done";
      if (this.step === n) return "In progress";
      return "Up next";
    },
    createProfile() {
      var name = this.profileName.trim();
      if (!name) return;
      this.$store.budget.createProfile(name);
      this.step = Math.max(this.step, 2);
    },
    addDraft() { this.accountDrafts.push({ name: "", type: "checking", balance: "" }); },
    removeDraft(i) { this.accountDrafts.splice(i, 1); },
    hasValidDraft() {
      return this.accountDrafts.some(function (r) { return r.name.trim(); });
    },
    parseDollars(s) {
      if (window.PBCalc) {
        var v = window.PBCalc.parseAmountCents(s);
        if (isFinite(v)) return v;
      }
      var n = Number(String(s || "").replace(/[$,\s]/g, ""));
      return isFinite(n) ? Math.round(n * 100) : 0;
    },
    createAccounts() {
      var self = this;
      this.accountDrafts.forEach(function (r) {
        if (!r.name.trim()) return;
        self.$store.budget.addAccount({
          name: r.name.trim(),
          type: r.type,
          openingBalance: self.parseDollars(r.balance),
        });
      });
      this.step = Math.max(this.step, 3);
    },
    applyTemplate() {
      var tpl = this.templates.find(function (t) { return t.id === this.selectedTemplate; }, this);
      if (!tpl) return;
      var self = this;
      tpl.groups.forEach(function (g) {
        var grp = self.$store.budget.addCategoryGroup(g.name);
        g.cats.forEach(function (catName) {
          self.$store.budget.addCategory({ groupId: grp.id, name: catName });
        });
      });
      this.$store.budget.pushToast("Categories created — edit them anytime on /app/categories/.");
      this.step = 4;
    },
    skipTemplate() { this.step = 4; },
  };
}
</script>

<style>
  .welcome-steps { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: var(--space-md); }
  .welcome-step {
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-input);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    transition: border-color var(--t-fast), background var(--t-fast);
  }
  .welcome-step.is-current { border-left-color: var(--accent); }
  .welcome-step.is-done    { border-left-color: var(--ok); background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--ok) 4%, var(--bg-elevated)); }
  .welcome-step.is-future  { opacity: 0.6; }

  .welcome-step__head {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 36px minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }
  .welcome-step__num {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .welcome-step.is-current .welcome-step__num { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; }
  .welcome-step.is-done    .welcome-step__num { background: var(--ok); color: #fff; }
  .welcome-step.is-done    .welcome-step__num::before { content: "✓"; }
  .welcome-step.is-done    .welcome-step__num { font-size: 1.3rem; }
  .welcome-step.is-done    .welcome-step__num span { display: none; }

  .welcome-step__title {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    line-height: 1.15;
  }
  .welcome-step__status {
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    background: var(--bg-alt);
    border-radius: 999px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .welcome-step.is-current .welcome-step__status { color: var(--accent); background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent) 12%, var(--bg)); }
  .welcome-step.is-done    .welcome-step__status { color: var(--ok);     background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--ok) 14%, var(--bg)); }

  .welcome-step__body { color: var(--fg); }
  .welcome-step__body > p { margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm); color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .welcome-step__hint { margin: var(--space-sm) 0 0; color: var(--fg-muted); font-size: var(--fs-sm); }

  .welcome-templates {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  }
  @media (max-width: 899px) { .welcome-templates { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
  .welcome-template {
    text-align: left;
    background: var(--bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: var(--radius-input);
    padding: var(--space-md);
    cursor: pointer;
    font: inherit;
    color: inherit;
    transition: border-color var(--t-fast), background var(--t-fast);
  }
  .welcome-template:hover { background: var(--bg-alt); border-color: var(--accent); }
  .welcome-template.is-selected { border-left-color: var(--accent); background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent) 6%, var(--bg)); }
  .welcome-template h3 {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xs);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--fs-lg);
  }
  .welcome-template p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-2xs);
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: var(--fs-sm);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .welcome-template ul {
    margin: var(--space-2xs) 0 0;
    padding-left: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    font-size: var(--fs-xs);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
</style>
